{"tid":740821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人生差唔多三十年 終於揾到四個字可以應對所有不幸","createTime":"2018-07-13T07:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T07:57:10.000Z","uid":108450,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f176fddf88fdbe63b295f0180cfd974bffde21c0","tid":740821,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"事源連登仔對每樣野都有一個好獨特嘅睇法 經過琴晚幾個柏麗灣同埋幾個不幸事情既post 我終於領悟四個字比子華神既:『搵食姐 犯法呀 我想㗎』更強大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">預左㗎啦</span><br />\n<br />\n依四個字可以完美套用係任何情況 做倫敦金比人拉 預左㗎啦 做Mk 比人打預左㗎啦 買小米電器三日就收皮預左㗎啦 舉個例醫生可以咁樣回應一屍兩命既不幸家屬: 生仔有風險 一屍兩命預左㗎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然可能行唔出醫院門口 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果想加強語氣可以配合埋關我咩事 一齊使用效果更佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n真係好想聽子華神既語氣講一句 關我咩事 預。左。㗎。啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edce4782ab94a5016655812d33e74c6323ce9402","tid":740821,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你真係呢"},{"pid":"eb0e704acd477bf08f5ee013f179376c9aaa648e","tid":740821,"uid":108450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"真㗎 你試下去隔離d post 基本上咩都可以咁回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d64a424aa3c567c757ba8d165e626306ea0233","tid":740821,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"樓主on9<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你都預左有人咁講㗎